How to buy software
div()
Buying software is simple. The built-in 'store' command is used to purchase software. To purchase software, you need credits. Credits are earned by completing missions.
div()
* To get a list of software, run 'store list'. You'll see a list in the format <program name> (<cost> Cr.)".
* To buy a program, run 'store buy <program name>'. 
* To check your credit balance, run 'store balance'.
div()